ElementLabel: Serve these orders and notices to parties, alongside the application and other documents
Some documents are automatically sent out by the system to the people in the case. You do not need to upload them.
Select the orders and notices that were created at the gatekeeping stage that you would like to serve to parties

HintText: Upload the PD36Q letter that is used by your court. The letter explains to users how the case allocation process may differ as a result of the Watford model.
Upload the special arrangement template letter that is used by your court. The letter explains to users what special measures and individual support may be available.
Upload any additional documents in your service pack that are due to be sent to both applicant and respondent.
